Select all columns using the asterisk wildcard.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [x 1] [y 2] [z 3]] | polars into-df | polars select (polars col '*') | polars collect
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
